              <h1 class="page-title"><span property="schema:name" class="field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden">Meat free meat with maths</span>
</h1>
            
              
                      <a href="/content/list-by-author/Marianne+Freiberger">Marianne Freiberger</a>                <a class="plus-share-button" data-bs-toggle="tooltip" data-bs-placement="top" title="Share this page!"
           data-title="Meat free meat with maths" data-url="https://plus.maths.org/meat-free-meat-maths" data-description="Article from Plus">Share this page</a>
